      "description": "Summon one Large quasi-real horse-like mount on an unoccupied ground space within 30 feet for up to 1 hour. The steed uses Riding Horse statistics with Speed 100 feet, can be ridden by the caster or a chosen creature, has saddle, bit, and bridle equipment that vanishes if carried more than 10 feet away, ends early if the steed takes damage, and fades over 1 minute when the spell ends.",
